{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571610/extras/worm_attack.gif?t=1737498601\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Father of AI is an exploration driven survival adventure set in the post-apocalyptic wasteland, where your greatest asset is your robot companion ALAN.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571610/extras/boulder_push.gif?t=1737498601\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Escape the Wasteland</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Left to die in the middle of the wasteland, you are saved by a wandering robot that goes by the name of ALAN. Your only hope of escaping the wasteland is to put your trust in ALAN. Together, you will battle fearsome mutated creatures, navigate harsh terrain and survive in the unforgiving wasteland. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571610/extras/help_up_new.gif?t=1737498601\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Explore a hostile open world filled with secrets, mystery and danger. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Work together with ALAN to fight mutated creatures, navigate harsh terrain and defeat powerful bosses. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Survive in the desolate wasteland by seeking out food, water, and power for ALAN. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Upgrade ALAN with special abilities to increase his ability to navigate obstacles, optimise your chances of survival, or tear through wasteland foes. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571610/extras/fight_gif.gif?t=1737498601\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2571610?